quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,53,"“Nena (kwa iwo mau anga akuti): “E inu akapolo anga! Amene mwadzichitira chinyengo, musataye mtima ndi chifundo cha Allah. Ndithu Allah amakhululuka machimo onse. Ndithu Iye Ngokhululuka kwambiri, Wachisoni chosatha.”"
  39,54,"“Ndipo tembenukirani kwa Mbuye wanu, ndipo m’gonjereni chilango chisadakudzereni. Ndipo zitatero, sim’dzapulumutsidwa"
  39,55,"“Ndipo tsatirani zabwino, zimene zavumbulutsidwa kwa inu kuchokera kwa Mbuye wanu chisadakufikeni chilango mwadzidzidzi pomwe inu simukudziwa!”"
  39,56,"“Kuti mzimu usadzanene: “Kalanga ine! Mzomwe sindidalabadire kumbali ya Allah; ndithu ndidali mmodzi wa ochitira chibwana (zinthu za chipembedzo).”"
  39,57,"“Kapena ungadzanene: “Allah akadandiongola, ndithu ndikadakhala mwa oopa (Allah).”"
  39,58,"“Kapena kunena utaona chilango: “Ndikadatha kubwerera (pa dziko lapansi), ndikadakhala mmodzi wa ochita zabwino.”"
  39,59,"“(Adzauzidwa: “Nchiyani iwe?) Ndithu zidakufika zisonyezo Zanga, ndipo udazitsutsa ndi kudzitukumula; ndipo udali mmodzi wa okanira.”"
  39,60,"“Ndipo tsiku la Qiyâma udzawaona omwe adamnamizira Allah, nkhope zawo zili zakuda. Kodi Jahannam simalo a odzitukumula"
  39,61,"“Ndipo Allah adzawapulumutsa amene adamuopa, chifukwa cha kupambana kwawo. Zoipa sizikawakhudza, ndipo iwo sakadandaula"
  39,62,"“Allah ndiye Mlengi wa chilichonse, ndipo Iye ndi Myang’aniri wa chilichonse"
  39,63,"“Makiyi a kumwamba ndi pansi ali kwa Iye. Ndipo amene akanira zisonyezo za Allah, iwo ndiwo oluza, (otaika)"